title: Efficiency W/full kitchen
posting_body: ['Efficiency apartment available for ONE single person with regular employment.', 'Available NOW.', 'Great location, Coral Ridge Isles on N.E. 18th', 'Ave. just north of Commercial Blvd.', 'Located in a quiet 6 unit apartment building (nice neighbors).', 'Features coin laundry room and assigned parking space.', 'City bus stop located right next door.', 'Ground floor unit with full kitchen and full bath with Shower.', ' Building features concrete walls in between apartments (great noise barrier).', 'Unit features\\new hurricane impact windows, New a/c wall unit.', 'Recently painted.', 'Rear door offers backyard access.', 'Water and trash included -  tenant pays electric.', '****Deal directly with the Owner/landlord and save on move-in costs.', 'Total move-in is 1st mo.+ $1000 security deposit=$2,000.00.', 'Application ($30) - +background/criminal check required.', 'Available 8/1.', 'sorry~ No pets, no smokers& No prior evictions.', '$1000/mo. call nine54-776-6121.', 'NO emails or text messages please, call and leave message, tell a little bit about yourself and leave call back number.']
